MIME/DecodeText version 0.01
============================


The perl module MIME::DecodeText allow to decode a text string
which was composed of a few differently encoded parts and plain
text parts. The 'spase' character is used as parts separator.

Please report any bugs/suggestions to Vlad Danego <vlad@al.lg.ua>

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:

   MIME::Base64
   MIME::QuotedPrint

